---
// Mid-page DominikOS showcase: the recruiter-friendly "here's what it is"
// surface. Crawlable links, restrained copy, zero heavy assets.
---

<section id="dominikos" class="section bg-dark os-showcase" aria-labelledby="dominikos-heading">
  <h2 id="dominikos-heading" class="head-text os-head">
    Prefer to explore? <span>Boot DominikOS</span>
  </h2>

  <p class="os-lede">
    I rebuilt my portfolio as a retro desktop operating system — windows, taskbar,
    boot screen and all. Everything on this page lives in there too, plus a few
    things that don't fit on a web page.
  </p>

  <ul class="os-features">
    <li>
      <span class="os-feature-title">Desktop</span>
      <span class="os-feature-desc">Draggable windows, Start menu, my projects &amp; CV as apps</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="os-feature-title">2D game</span>
      <span class="os-feature-desc">Walk my career timeline as an explorable pixel-art town</span>
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="os-feature-title">Pinball</span>
      <span class="os-feature-desc">An original cyberpunk table — chase the high score</span>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="os-actions">
    <a class="os-boot-btn" href="/os/?boot=chooser">
      <span aria-hidden="true">&#x23FB;</span> Boot DominikOS
    </a>
    <span class="os-deep p-text">
      or jump straight to the
      <a href="/os/?boot=desktop">desktop</a> ·
      <a href="/os/?boot=game">game</a>
    </span>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .os-showcase {
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .os-head {
    color: var(--white-color);
  }

  .os-head span {
    color: #22d3ee;
  }

  .os-lede {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 56ch;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    font-size: var(--text-md);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
  }

  .os-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2.25rem;
  }

  .os-features li {
    width: 15rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .os-feature-title {
    color: var(--white-color);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-caps);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .os-feature-desc {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.66);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  .os-actions {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.9rem;
  }

  .os-boot-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 0.95rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #43c258, #2f9e44 55%, #28863a);
    border: 1px solid #1f6e2f;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    text-shadow: 0 1px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45), 0 4px 14px rgba(31, 110, 47, 0.45);
    transition: filter 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .os-boot-btn:hover,
  .os-boot-btn:focus-visible {
    filter: brightness(1.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .os-deep {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .os-deep a {
    color: #9fd8e8;
  }
</style>
